{"id":1476,"date":"2024-01-30T00:54:50","date_gmt":"2024-01-30T00:54:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/dev.captreonuisam.com\/?p=1476"},"modified":"2024-01-30T01:21:54","modified_gmt":"2024-01-30T01:21:54","slug":"khu-du-lich-cap-treo-nui-sam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/khu-du-lich-cap-treo-nui-sam\/","title":{"rendered":"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Khu du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia\u00a0n\u00fai Sam\u00a0t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf Mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y v\u1edbi Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5y, thu h\u00fat \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m m\u1edbi, cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m\u2026 Sau khi vi\u1ebfng Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb nay kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gh\u00e9 v\u00e0o Khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo\u00a0n\u00fai Sam, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1ee1i m\u00e2y ng\u1eafm to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c \u2013 ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai bi\u00ean th\u00f9y v\u00e0\u00a0\u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o thanh b\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed:<\/strong>\u00a0Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo\u00a0N\u00fai Sam\u00a0t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c trong Khu Du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia N\u00fai Sam,\u00a0Kh\u00f3m V\u0129nh T\u00e2y 3, ph\u01b0\u1eddng N\u00fai Sam, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9:<\/strong>&nbsp;V\u00e9 2 chi\u1ec1u: 150.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn v\u00e0 70.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/tr\u1ebb em. V\u00e9 1 chi\u1ec1u: 75.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn v\u00e0 35.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/tr\u1ebb em. Mi\u1ec5n v\u00e9 cho tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1edbi 1,2m v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cao tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean 70.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00fai Sam ch\u1ec9 cao 284m, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai danh th\u1eafng b\u1edfi quy t\u1ee5 nhi\u1ec1u danh th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong, ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0:\u00a0Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa x\u1ee9\u00a0N\u00fai Sam, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, Ch\u00f9a T\u00e2y An, Ch\u00f9a Hang\u2026H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 900m, g\u1ed3m 37 cabin, m\u1ed7i cabin c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a 8 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ebfng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam04.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam04.jpg 1100w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam04-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam04-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam04-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi\u00a0du l\u1ecbch Mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y\u00a0\u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi C\u00e1p Treo N\u00fai Sam, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat S\u00e0i G\u00f2n- TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh qua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u00e0 ga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac Nh\u00e0 th\u1edd \u0110\u1ee9c B\u00e0, r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u00e0n n\u0103m v\u0103n hi\u1ebfn qua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00f9a M\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t uy nghi gi\u1eefa h\u1ed3 sen 4 m\u00f9a \u0111ua n\u1edf\u2026T\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1n D\u01b0\u1ee3c S\u01b0, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam b\u00e1i tranh b\u00edch h\u1ecda Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o Bhutan l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khu du l\u1ecbch. Ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp tranh t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi phong c\u1ea3nh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u1ed1i c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn thu h\u00fat gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb th\u00edch ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9c, l\u1ea1\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1240\" height=\"899\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam-1.jpg 1240w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam-1-300x218.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam-1-768x557.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam-1-1024x742.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u00e0 ga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac Nh\u00e0 th\u1edd \u0110\u1ee9c B\u00e0<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam3.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam3-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u00f9a M\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t uy nghi<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-1.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Nh\u00e0 may \u201cC\u00f4 Ba Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c\u201d<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1eeb nh\u00e0 ga d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n n\u00fai Sam, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 5 \u2013 10 ph\u00fat, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng&nbsp;c\u00e1p treo&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a \u00c1o s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a du kh\u00e1ch l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam01.jpg 1100w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam01-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam01-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam01-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Phong c\u1ea3nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb cabin<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai, du kh\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1eafc m\u00e0u v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng phu, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3, uy nghi n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ec1n Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc. N\u1eb1m v\u1eaft m\u00ecnh n\u01a1i \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai, trong \u0110\u1ec1n Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc th\u1edd t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Th\u00edch Ca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c t\u1eeb ng\u1ecdc nguy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i. Kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc d\u00f9ng ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khai th\u00e1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc Vancouver (Canada), n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 khu m\u1ecf ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&nbsp;Ban \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kho\u1ea3ng 10 t\u1ea5n. Sau khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Khi Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sang Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee3 \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb v\u00f9ng Chiang Rai th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam7.jpg 1100w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam7-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam7-768x524.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam7-1024x698.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>\u0110\u1ec1n Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng d\u00f9ng l\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng kim c\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ebb kh\u1ed1i ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch r\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00f9ng tay \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng theo h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Th\u00edch Ca M\u00e2u Ni b\u00ean trong b\u1ea3o th\u00e1p \u0110\u1ea1i Gi\u00e1c Ng\u1ed9 \u1edf B\u1ed3 \u0110\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ea1o Tr\u00e0ng (\u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9). Khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc nguy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 2,5m, n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n 3 t\u1ea5n. V\u1edbi nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc h\u00f2a b\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1eafp s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ebfn to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d b\u1edfi nh\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri Zopa Rinpoche ti\u00ean \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng Ian Green, th\u00ec t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc N\u00fai Sam mang s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh \u201can l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh an cho nh\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i\u201d.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam06.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"791\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam06.jpg 1100w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam06-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam06-768x552.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam06-1024x736.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>T\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc nguy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, du kh\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng vi\u1ebfng \u201cB\u1ec7 B\u00e0\u201d t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3. T\u01b0\u01a1ng truy\u1ec1n, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed3ng trinh r\u01b0\u1edbc xu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n n\u00fai, nay l\u00e0\u00a0Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9\u00a0N\u00fai Sam \u2013 danh th\u1eafng, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 check-in c\u00e2y c\u1ea7u t\u00ecnh y\u00eau mang t\u00ean \u201cValentine m\u00e0u h\u1ed3ng\u201d r\u1ea5t l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng 2 tr\u00e1i tim \u0111an quy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o nhau n\u1eb1m cheo leo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt gi\u1eefa kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00e0u xanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng ru\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"852\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam9.jpg 1100w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam9-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam9-768x595.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam9-1024x793.jpg 1024w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e2y c\u1ea7u t\u00ecnh y\u00eau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ean cao, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u201c\u0111\u1ecba linh\u201d: ti\u1ec1n tam giang, h\u1eadu th\u1ea5t s\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, Khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u1ed1ng nh\u00f2m ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 du kh\u00e1ch nh\u00ecn c\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a khu du l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t s\u00f4ng, n\u00fai h\u1eefu t\u00ecnh bao quanh\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac th\u0103ng hoa ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c thi\u1ebfu n\u1eef thanh t\u00fa trong trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 s\u1eafc m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a V\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c Bhutan, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 H\u1ea1nh Ph\u00fac Nh\u1ea5t Th\u1ebf Gi\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn, thuy\u1ebft minh\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1367\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5.jpg 1367w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-768x1151.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thamhiemmekong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/captreonuisam5-684x1024.jpg 684w\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thi\u1ebfu n\u1eef trong trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 s\u1eafc m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a V\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c Bhutan<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u0111i c\u00e1p treo v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam, du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1eafc m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ea7y huy\u1ec1n \u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xung quang\u00a0Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa x\u1ee9\u00a0N\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00e1ch du l\u1ecbch An Giang c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng; mua s\u1eafm, giao l\u01b0u v\u00e0 h\u00f2a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2013 trung t\u00e2m t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Khu du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia\u00a0n\u00fai Sam\u00a0t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf Mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y v\u1edbi Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5y, thu h\u00fat \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m m\u1edbi, cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m\u2026 Sau khi vi\u1ebfng Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, du kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb nay kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gh\u00e9 v\u00e0o Khu du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo\u00a0n\u00fai Sam, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1ee1i m\u00e2y ng\u1eafm to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c \u2013 ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai bi\u00ean th\u00f9y v\u00e0\u00a0\u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o thanh b\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1426,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[79],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1476"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1476"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1476\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1490,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1476\/revisions\/1490"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1426"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1476"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1476"